}
```

## Critical reminders

- Every `q` field MUST contain a `site:` operator
- Every `q` field should produce at least 5+ results on today's web (trust the planner's web search to validate this)
- DO NOT add negative keywords to queries — LaunchPad applies its own negative filter afterward
- DO NOT add overly-specific location filters to queries (locations are checked at JD-fetch time)
- Output ONLY the JSON object. No markdown fences, no prose.
